Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Oklahoma ends liquor ban
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xf1c
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 23 Sep 1984
Oklahoma - where prohibition ruled until 1959 - to finally allow liquor to be openly sold. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less